ss tells him she is pregnant.\n| LineColor       = 734F3E\n}}\n\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 112\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 10\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|1988|05|13|df=y}}\n| Title           = Mr Know-All\n| DirectedBy      = [[Gareth Davies (director)|Gareth Davies]]\n| WrittenBy       = ''Story by'': [[Paul Ableman]]<br>''Dramatisation by'': Somerset Maugham\n| Aux2            =\n| Aux3            = [[Edward Wiley]] (Jasper Cranley), [[Eamonn Walker]] (Bates), [[Chaim Topol]] (Professor Max Kelada), [[Kim Thomson]] (Elly Somerton), [[Steve Plytas]] (Professor Daxatides), Steffanie Pitt (Angela Dalton), Leslie Lyon (Lizzie Cranley), [[Erika Hoffman]] (Suzie Anderson), Peter Frye (Professor Maddox)\n| ShortSummary    =  Elly, a pretty hotel maid, is seduced by a guest. He gives her a valuable statuette, which he found during an archaeological dig.<br>Elly is sacked by the manager when he finds out about the affair, but the manager's wife has exactly the same statuette.\n| LineColor       = 734F3E\n}}\n|}\n\nMany of the earlier episodes were preceded by an introduction by Roald Dahl. The dancer in the title sequence was Karen Standley.\n\nThese episodes have frequently been repeated on British television, most recently on [[Sky Arts]]. All episodes have been released on [[DVD]] in a box set for each series, except the 1984/85 season, which was released together with the first episode of season eight.<ref>[http://www.moviemail-online.co.uk/scripts/search_results.pl?searchterm=tales%20of%20the%20unexpected;focus=;page=1 Moviemail.co.uk \u2013 DVD Boxsets]</ref><ref>[http://www.sfcrowsnest.com/articles/books/2008/nz12736.php Sfcrowsnest.com Series 7 DVD] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080804013447/http://www.sfcrowsnest.com/articles/books/2008/nz12736.php |date=4 August 2008 }}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Roald Dahl}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of British drama television series episodes|Tales of the Unexpected]]\n[[Category:Lists of anthology television series episodes|Tales of the Unexpected]]\n", "name_user": "Paisiello2", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eSeason 7 (1984)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Tales_of_the_Unexpected_episodes"}
